description: Return the gateway status of the specified Analysis Services server instance.

subscription_id.description: A unique identifier for a Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

error.description: Error of the list gateway status.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the Azure Resource group of which a given Analysis Services server is part. This name must be at least 1 character in length, and no more than 90.

server_name.description: The name of the Analysis Services server.
